New Zealand 5th wicket partnership (Styris/Vincent): 50 off 71 balls, 51 minutes
New Zealand 10th wicket partnership (Vincent/Bond): 50 off 21 balls, 14 minutes
India were fined 1 over for a slow over rate
India Innings: 50 off 65 balls, 44 minutes; 100 off 157 balls, 106 minutes; 150 off 213 balls, 145 minutes

India 2nd wicket partnership (Sehwag/Dravid): 50 off 87 balls, 56 minutes
V Sehwag: 50 off 80 balls, 103 minutes; 100 off 129 balls, 165 minutes
SE Bond bowled a no ball that went for 4

stories.title: Thriller gives win to India but lessons to NZ
stories.summary:
Virender Sehwag: second century of the series sets India up for victory  
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
It was the result the National Bank Series has been crying out for and it was a genuine thriller at Eden Park as India got home over New Zealand by one wicket
